# User surface parity

Hidden failure mode: Persian or Toman fixed in the bot only while cabinet/miniapp still show `₽` or Cyrillic.

## Same slice

| Change | Touch at least |
|--------|----------------|
| Price/balance keys in `fa.json` | Bot handler **and** `app/cabinet/routes/**` **and** `app/webapi/routes/miniapp.py` |
| Display amounts | `texts.format_price` / API fields built via `settings.format_price` |

If one file per commit is required by `localization-upstream.mdc`, note in PR: **cabinet/miniapp follow-up** or extend the commit to cover all three.

## Out of parity scope

- Admin Telegram panels (separate track; `get_texts(db_user.language)`)
- Payment provider internals (`app/handlers/balance/**`, `app/services/payment/**`)
- Admin group notifications (`AdminNotificationService` — Persian per `fa-i18n-status.mdc`)
